{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3304","heading":"Transfer fraudulent as to a debt to the United States","label":"3304 Transfer fraudulent as to a debt to the United States","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/ptVI/ch176/schD","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective 180 days after , and applicable with respect to certain actions for debts owed the United States pending in court on that effective date, see , set out as a note under .Nov. 29, 1990section 3631 of Pub. L. 101–647section 3001 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Debt Arising Before Transfer","label":"a .—Debt Arising Before Transfer","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor makes the transfer or incurs the obligation without receiving a reasonably equivalent value in exchange for the transfer or obligation; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor is insolvent at that time or the debtor becomes insolvent as a result of the transfer or obligation; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the transfer was made to an insider for an antecedent debt, the debtor was insolvent at the time; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the insider had reasonable cause to believe that the debtor was insolvent.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Transfers Without Regard to Date of Judgment","label":"b .—Transfers Without Regard to Date of Judgment","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"with actual intent to hinder, delay, or defraud a creditor; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F1%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"was engaged or was about to engage in a business or a transaction for which the remaining assets of the debtor were unreasonably small in relation to the business or transaction; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/1/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F1%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"intended to incur, or believed or reasonably should have believed that he would incur, debts beyond his ability to pay as they became due.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the transfer or obligation was to an insider;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor retained possession or control of the property transferred after the transfer;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the transfer or obligation was disclosed or concealed;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"before the transfer was made or obligation was incurred, the debtor had been sued or threatened with suit;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"E","heading":null,"label":"E","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/E","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FE","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the transfer was of substantially all the debtor’s assets;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"F","heading":null,"label":"F","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/F","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FF","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor absconded;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"G","heading":null,"label":"G","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/G","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FG","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor removed or concealed assets;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"H","heading":null,"label":"H","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/H","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FH","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the value of the consideration received by the debtor was reasonably equivalent to the value of the asset transferred or the amount of the obligation incurred;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor was insolvent or became insolvent shortly after the transfer was made or the obligation was incurred;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"J","heading":null,"label":"J","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/J","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FJ","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the transfer occurred shortly before or shortly after a substantial debt was incurred; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"K","heading":null,"label":"K","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2/K","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3304/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3304%2Fb%2F2%2FK","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the debtor transferred the essential assets of the business to a lienor who transferred the assets to an insider of the debtor.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
